ogenomics<!--]--><!--[-->, <!--]--><!--]--><!--[--><!--[-->genotoxicity<!--]--><!--[-->, <!--]--><!--]--><!--[--><!--[-->biomarker<!--]--><!--[-->, <!--]--><!--]--><!--[--><!--[-->high-throughput (HT) approaches<!--]--><!----><!--]--><!--]--></p><!--]--><!--[--><p class="h5">Citation</p><p>Li H-H, Yauk CL, Chen R, Hyduke DR, Williams A, Frötschl R, Ellinger-Ziegelbauer H, Pettit S, Aubrecht J and Fornace Jr. AJ (2019) <!--[-->TGx-DDI, a Transcriptomic Biomarker for Genotoxicity Hazard Assessment of Pharmaceuticals and Environmental Chemicals<!--]-->. <i>Front. Big Data</i> 2:36. doi: <a class="Summary__doi notranslate" target="_blank" href="http://dx.doi.org/10.3389/fdata.2019.00036" data-event="articleSummary-a-doi">10.3389/fdata.2019.00036</a></p><!--]--><!----><!--[--><!--[--><p class="h5">Received</p><p>26 April 2019</p><!--]--><!----><!--[--><p class="h5">Accepted</p><p>17 September 2019</p><!--]--><!--[--><p class="h5">Published</p><p>08 October 2019</p><!--]--><!----><!----><!----><p class="h5">Volume</p><p>2 - 2019</p><!----><!--[--><p class="h5">Edited by</p><!--[--><p class="notranslate"> Yvonne Will, Pfizer, United States</p><!--]--><!--]--><!--[--><p class="h5">Reviewed by</p><!--[--><p class="notranslate"> Julia Rager, University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill, United States; Matthew Thomas Martin, Pfizer, United States</p><!--]--><!--]--><!--]--><!--[--><p class="h5">Updates</p><button class="CrossmarkUpdates" data-target="crossmark" data-event="crossmarkUpdates-btn-openModalCrossmark"><img class="CrossmarkUpdates__img" src="/ap-2024/images/crossmark_color.webp" alt="Crossmark icon"><p>Check for updates</p></button><!--]--><p class="h5"> Copyright </p><div class="Summary__copyright"><p class="Summary__copyright__text">© 2019 Li, Yauk, Chen, Hyduke, Williams, Frötschl, Ellinger-Ziegelbauer, Pettit, Aubrecht and Fornace. </p><!--[--><p>This is an open-access article distributed under the terms of the <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/